name: Pink Diamond Energy
description:
First seen on Lil Uzi's Forehead... the 24 Million Dollar Diamond is back.

Here's your chance to place a pink diamond on your skull.

First person to tweet a photo with the face filter will receive a $25 Giftcard towards the purchase of a 3D print (Thunder Bolt, Smiley,...future releases)

Bonus points if you tweet me photos of the face filter on inanimate objects. 

Twitter: @killjoyartclub
